		{"STR_BASE_DEFENSES_INITIATED", "DEFENSIVE BATTERIES FIRING"},
		{"STR_GRAV_SHIELD_REPELS_UFO", "REPULSOR BEAM REPELS ENEMIES!"},
		{"STR_UFO_DESTROYED", "IS BLOWN TO PIECES!"},
		{"STR_SELL_ITEMS_SACK_PERSONNEL", "Fence Yer Stuff Away!"},
		{"STR_SELL_SACK", "Deal"},
		{"STR_UFO_CRASH_RECOVERY", "SEIZE YER BOOTY!"},
		{"STR_UFO_CRASH_RECOVERY_BRIEFING", "We arrived at the crash site, Cap'n! Likely many of those scurvy dogs survived the landing and won't give away their booty without a fight. Too bad for 'em!  If, however, things go south for our crew, remember that anyone not onboard when you takeoff will be lost!"},
		{"STR_UFO_GROUND_ASSAULT", "GROUND ASSAULT!"},
		{"STR_UFO_GROUND_ASSAULT_BRIEFING", "Excellent, Cap'n! We managed to sneakily land next to their ship. Any goods they are carrying are undamaged and ours for the taking! Yarr!"},
		{"STR_BASE_DEFENSE", "HIDEOUT DEFENSE"},
		{"STR_BASE_UC_", "HIDEOUT> {0}"},
		{"STR_BASE_DEFENSE_BRIEFING", "Enemy dogs have targeted our base and right now it's being attacked! Time to make them pay for such a mistake... or abandon this ship. Of course, our valiant crew will be left behind. Your choice, Cap'n."},
		{"STR_ALIEN_BASE_ASSAULT", "SECRET BASE ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_ALIEN_BASE_ASSAULT_ETHEREAL", "SECRET BASE ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_ALIEN_BASE_ASSAULT_ACADEMY", "SECRET BASE ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_ALIEN_BASE_ASSAULT_GUILD", "SECRET BASE ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_ALIEN_BASE_ASSAULT_CHURCH", "SECRET BASE ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_ALIEN_BASE_ASSAULT_BRIEFING", "A secret operation of one of the Factions is being run here. Its continuation makes the local Govt look weak, thus cutting heavily into OUR protection funds. However, assaulting an enemy Hideout is a serious undertaking, and requires a major investment of resources. If we'll abort this mission, it will costs us -400 Infamy. We will be using backdoor, so we can't bring any tanks. Time to crash this party, Cap'n!{NEWLINE}Depth: Average."},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_OUTPOST_ASSAULT", "NINJA OUTPOST ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_OUTPOST_ASSAULT_BRIEFING", "{NEWLINE}The Sky Ninjas have established a forward base of operations here. We better root them out, before it grows into something more dangerous. Thankfully, there isn't too many of them here, but we can surely expect lots of point defense."},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_OUTPOST_2_ASSAULT", "NINJA FIREBASE ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_OUTPOST_2_ASSAULT_BRIEFING", "{NEWLINE}The Sky Ninja works in this area are complete. They have dug themselves in quite heavily, and their AA defense bars direct landing. Regardless, their strategic-range missiles stationed here rack them up an impressive Infamy score each day, which is of course at our cost."},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_1_ASSAULT", "NINJA AIRFIELD ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_1_ASSAULT_BRIEFING", "{NEWLINE}The Sky Ninja base is protected by dangerous anti-air defenses, so we must approach it on foot, across open field. It's gonna be a shooting gallery, and we're the targets, so we'd better deploy some countermeasures. Thankfully, we didn't detect any heavy artillery emplacements."},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_2_ASSAULT", "NINJA FORTRESS ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_2_ASSAULT_BRIEFING", "{NEWLINE}The Sky Ninjas managed to turn this base into a very dangerous stronghold. As usual, we have to approach it on foot. Aside from strengthening ground and aerial defenses, they also dug out an underground level. Difficult access to that underground level, as well as various obstacles will make the use of tanks difficult, if we take them."},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_2_UNDERGROUND_ASSAULT", "NINJA FORTRESS UNDERGROUND"},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_UNDERGROUND_ASSAULT_BRIEFING", "{NEWLINE}We have infiltrated into the bowels of this Ninja base. All that's left is to purge them here, and their fortress will fall - permanently. Then we can claim this area for our trade operations."},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_HQ_1_ASSAULT", "NINJA HQ ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_HQ_2_ASSAULT", "NINJA HQ ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_HQ_3_ASSAULT", "NINJA HQ ASSAULT"},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_HQ_ASSAULT_BRIEFING", "This is the location of the Ninja expeditionary headquarters. It is very heavily fortified and dug deep underground. Attacking it will be an extremely difficult ordeal."},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_HQ_HANGAR_ASSAULT", "NINJA HQ HANGAR"},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_HQ_HANGAR_ASSAULT_BRIEFING", "The cavernous underground hangar of the base lies in front of us. In the darkness we can make out the shape of a monster blocking our way: a Mobile Fortress is parked here. We cannot proceed further before defeating it."},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_HQ_UNDERGROUND_ASSAULT", "NINJA HQ INNER SANCTUM"},
		{"STR_NINJA_BASE_HQ_UNDERGROUND_ASSAULT_BRIEFING", "This is it, the last bastion of Ninja defense. Eradicating it will put an end to their bid for world supremacy, however we can still expect their sporadic attacks coming from Jillsville."},
		{"STR_NINJA_HQ_DONE", "Ninja HQ Destroyed"},
		{"STR_NINJA_HQ_DONE_UFOPEDIA", "{NEWLINE}This feat has undermined the resolve of the Sky Ninjas. Their higher ranks will surrender to our enslavement now.{NEWLINE}+2000 Infamy."},
		{"STR_MISSION_NINJA_RAID", "Ninja Raid"},
		{"STR_NINJA_RAID_SITE", "Ninja Raid Site"},
		{"STR_NINJA_RAID_SITE_ALERT", "Ninja Raid!"},
		{"STR_NINJA_RAID_SITE_BRIEFING", "{NEWLINE}The Sky Ninjas are stealing our thunder! They raided an installation belonging to the Big Factions and are in the process of turning everything into scrap metal as we speak. (Is scrap metal even worth such effort?) If we're to interfere, we have to be quick, it will take them 8 hours at most. But if we ignore this, our Infamy will take a hit."},
		{"STR_CYDONIA_BRIEFING", "Everything is ready for the grand finale, Cap'n. Time to bring down the false gods and seize the power of the Ancients!"},
		{"STR_TERROR_MISSION", "MUTANT POGROM"},
		{"STR_TERROR_MISSION_NO_PENALTY", "MUTANT POGROM (Freelance)"},
		{"STR_TERROR_MISSION_BRIEFING", "The Mutant Alliance has called for our support! We have to stop this Pogrom and save as many Free Mutants as possible. If we ignore this mission, a -1000 Infamy penalty will be inflicted upon us by the Alliance.{NEWLINE}Weather: Temperate, Cold Snaps possible. Sea: Stormy."},
		{"STR_TERROR_MISSION_NO_PENALTY_BRIEFING", "The local mutants are calling for help! The forces of evil decided it's time to curb the mutant population and launched a pogrom at this city. They thought it'd be like shooting fish in the barrel - they were wrong! Time to enter the stage and kill all these bastards off! This is surely going to make headlines, plus, whatever these evildoers are packing, is ours for the taking!{NEWLINE}Weather: Temperate, Cold Snaps possible. Sea: Stormy."},
		{"STR_MISSION_HUNT_SECRET_BASE_DEFENSE", "Secret Base Defense"},
		{"STR_MISSION_HUNT_NINJA_BASE_OUTPOST_DEFENSE", "Ninja Hideout Defense"},
		{"STR_MISSION_HUNT_NINJA_BASE_1_DEFENSE", "Ninja Hideout Defense"},
		{"STR_MISSION_HUNT_NINJA_BASE_2_DEFENSE", "Ninja Hideout Defense"},
		{"STR_MISSION_ERIDIAN_TERROR", "Mutant Culling"},
		{"STR_MISSION_ERIDIAN_TERROR_MSDF", "Mutant Suppression"},
		{"STR_MISSION_ERIDIAN_TERROR_UFOPEDIA", "It seems like the uproar we have caused finally reached the ears of the Solar Governor, or whatever else organ it's using. A large ship full of Eridians has arrived to our solar system, and these savages have been tasked with quelling down Earth's mutants - which, knowing Eridian cavalier attitude towards chemical and biological weaponry, amounts to genocide. We might try to help the mutants, but we won't be able to stop the use of these weapons - only properly organized locals stand a chance to prevent such an attack."},
		{"STR_ERIDIAN_TERROR", "MUTANT CULLING"},
		{"STR_ERIDIAN_TERROR_MSDF", "MUTANT SUPPRESSION"},
		{"STR_ERIDIAN_TERROR_BRIEFING", "A warband of Eridians have used chemical weapons on a mutant population center! The locals had no means of defending themselves from this onslaught. The Mutant Alliance is desperate and is begging us for help, as they seem to have no-one better for the job. Refusing will cost us a 2000 Infamy hit, but if we go there, we're gonna need to use all we've got.{NEWLINE}Weather: TOXIC. Sea: Deadly."},
		{"STR_ERIDIAN_TERROR_MSDF_BRIEFING", "A warband of Eridians is attacking the free mutants! The MSDF managed to thwart a chemical weapon strike the Eridians were planning, but they can't do much to stop an invasion that is following. If we don't help them out, this will be a major disaster to our reputation (-1500).{NEWLINE}Weather: Temperate. Sea: Deadly."},
		{"STR_MISSION_NINJA_RAID_GOVT", "Attack on Govt"},
		{"STR_GOVT_BASE_DEFENSE", "Govt Base Defense"},
		{"STR_ALERT_GOVT_BASE_DEFENSE", "Friends in Govt Attacked!"},
		{"STR_GOVT_BASE_DEFENSE_BRIEFING", "{NEWLINE}This Govt compound, commanded by a General supporting our cause, is under a heavy Sky Ninja assault. We will take defensive positions around the compound. The General says he will personally lead a counterattack of his most loyal soldiers. We estimate he will wait around 8 turns for maximum dramatic effect. We'd better not get him killed. If all else fails, we can escape to his bunker and convince him to hunker down - this will at least cut our losses. We have only several hours to attend this mission."},
		{"STR_MISSION_NINJA_CRAWLER_RAID_GOVT", "Attack on Govt"},
		{"STR_NINJA_CRAWLER_RAID_GOVT", "Attack on Govt"},
		{"STR_NINJA_CRAWLER_RAID_GOVT_BRIEFING", "{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}The Sky Ninjas are attacking Govt officers! Why should we care? Because these particular officers support our cause in their country, and if the Ninjas manage to eliminate these guys... Well I don't have to explain, do I!{NEWLINE}Warning: we have only several hours to get to the site."},
