		{"STR_UAC_SECURITY_DRONE_ARMOR_UFOPEDIA", "A light threaded vehicle, boldly designed for space exploration. Now these ancient machines haunt abandoned UAC bases. NV: 15. ThV: 35%."},
		{"STR_UAC_SECURITY_DRONE_UFOPEDIA", "A light threaded vehicle, boldly designed for space exploration. Now these ancient machines haunt abandoned UAC bases. NV: 15. ThV: 35%."},
		{"STR_CYBERSCARAB_ARMOR_UFOPEDIA", "This creepy drone is meant to stalk the battlefield and deliver special packages to enemy doorstep (packages not included). Its conical, armored hull makes it quite resistant to enemy fire and difficult to spot (CAMO: 25/5). However, it isn't much of a spotter itself (DV: 20, NV: 10, ThV: 50%). It can be used with the Gnome Tecnovator armor."},
		{"STR_RECON_DRONE_ARMOR_UFOPEDIA", "Invisible and silent (CAMO: 25/7), it circles over the battlefield and hunts down enemies. Unarmed and fragile as it is, it's a terror of the sky none the less. It's packed with intel-gathering optronics (NV: 16, ThV: 50%, SPOT: 3, AyPhone) and switchable floodlight. It can be used with the Gnome Tecnovator armor."},
