		{"STR_FORTUNA_ANOMALY_EVENT", "Unspeakable Anomaly Stabilizes"},
		{"STR_FORTUNA_ANOMALY_EVENT_DESC", "The Anomaly seems to be running out of energy, its dreamlike qualities receding and everything becoming more physical. The ship inside the Anomaly is looking almost completely normal now, although it has changed. We've found the library and its interesting contents, including the 'Gray Codex'. But there also was a shortie stranger inside! She didn't resist arrest. We think the anomaly can be completely collapsed by sucking out the rest of its energy through high voltage cables."},
		{"STR_FUEGO_ANOMALY_EVENT", "Entrapping Anomaly Stabilizes"},
		{"STR_FUEGO_ANOMALY_EVENT_DESC", "The Anomaly seems to be running out of energy, its dreamlike qualities receding and everything becoming more physical. The ship inside the Anomaly is looking almost completely normal now, although it has changed. We've found the Captain's Quarters and they're full of treasure! There was also a snazy uniform and 3 Gal-sized space suits, and of course the 'Golden Codex'! We think the anomaly can be completely collapsed by sucking out the rest of its energy through high voltage cables."},
		{"STR_METALLO_ANOMALY_EVENT", "Tempestuous Anomaly Stabilizes"},
		{"STR_METALLO_ANOMALY_EVENT_DESC", "The Anomaly seems to be running out of energy, its dreamlike qualities receding and everything becoming more physical. The ship inside the Anomaly is looking almost completely normal now, although it has changed. We've found the armory and retrieved its contents. We've also found the 'Red Codex'!... and a weird skull. We think the anomaly can be completely collapsed by sucking out the rest of its energy through high voltage cables."},
		{"STR_VENTURA_ANOMALY_EVENT", "Tranquil Anomaly Stabilizes"},
		{"STR_VENTURA_ANOMALY_EVENT_DESC", "The Anomaly seems to be running out of energy, its dreamlike qualities receding and everything becoming more physical. The ship inside the Anomaly is looking almost completely normal now, although it has changed. We've found the medbay and retrieved its contents (including 3 occupied pods). We've also found the 'Green Codex'! We think the anomaly can be completely collapsed by sucking out the rest of its energy through high voltage cables."},
		{"STR_FORTUNA_ANOMALY_TENSION_EVENT", "Unspeakable Anomaly Acts Up"},
		{"STR_FORTUNA_ANOMALY_TENSION_EVENT_DESC", "The activity within the Anomaly was picking up rapidly for the last few hours, and then seemingly reached its apex! The crew was hit by a wave of nightmarish visions! Of course, I was taking notes.{NEWLINE}[-210 Infamy, +1 Mad Scribblings]"},
		{"STR_FUEGO_ANOMALY_TENSION_EVENT", "Entrapping Anomaly Acts Up"},
		{"STR_FUEGO_ANOMALY_TENSION_EVENT_DESC", "The activity within the Anomaly was picking up rapidly for the last few hours, and then seemingly reached its apex! It was a massive shudder that apparently was felt within the radius of many miles and caused many witnesses to, well, spontaneously climax. This will make us famous! Too bad it was so strong that some ceilings collapsed as well.{NEWLINE}[+300 Infamy, +30 Big Rocks]"},
		{"STR_METALLO_ANOMALY_TENSION_EVENT", "Tempestuous Anomaly Acts Up"},
		{"STR_METALLO_ANOMALY_TENSION_EVENT_DESC", "The activity within the Anomaly was picking up rapidly for the last few hours, and then seemingly reached its apex! It got so hot that it caused many minor fires, and we need to cover the damages.{NEWLINE}[-$25,000]"},
		{"STR_VENTURA_ANOMALY_TENSION_EVENT", "Tranquil Anomaly Acts Up"},
		{"STR_VENTURA_ANOMALY_TENSION_EVENT_DESC", "The activity within the Anomaly was picking up rapidly for the last few hours, and then seemingly reached its apex! For a moment it seemed like it was about to explode, but then it slackened and some... really... vile... stuff leaked out of it... But hey, some useful things seem to be floating in it! Hmmm...{NEWLINE}[+15 Cleaning Bills, +7 Junk Piles]"},
