		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_500_GOBLIN_ZAXX", "Liquidation Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_500_GOBLIN_ZAXX_DA", "Redeem Liquidation Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_500_GOBLIN_ZAXX_UFOPEDIA", "{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Gained for liquidating Goblin Zaxx's unwanted assets.{NEWLINE}The strange creature's head is supposed to be a message of impending doom. An expensive one. Very. Artificial? Of course it is.{NEWLINE}Redeem value: 500 Goblin Zaxx's Bounty Tokens"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_1250_GOBLIN_ZAXX", "Goblin Zaxx IOUs"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_1250_GOBLIN_ZAXX_DA", "Redeem Zaxx IOUs"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_1250_GOBLIN_ZAXX_UFOPEDIA", "{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}This briefcase stores a bunch of magical papers that will supposedly gain an immense value sometime in the future. How does it work, we don't know, and this knowledge is probably useless to us since we don't run a major banking cartel.{NEWLINE}Redeem value: 1250 Goblin Zaxx's Bounty Tokens + 20 Golden Chips"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_50_JACK", "Jack's Badge of Favor"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_50_JACK_DA", "Redeem Badge of Favor"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_50_JACK_UFOPEDIA", "{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Bestowed upon those who have obtained a favor from Jack, as the name implies.{NEWLINE}Redeem value: 50 Jack's Bounty Tokens."},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_150_JACK", "Aircar Race Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_150_JACK_DA", "Redeem Aircar Race Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_150_JACK_UFOPEDIA", "You have won an Aircar Race and a lot of money for Jack.{NEWLINE}Redeem value: 150 Jack's Bounty Tokens each."},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_200_JACK", "Execution Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_200_JACK_DA", "Redeem Execution Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_200_JACK_UFOPEDIA", "{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Gained for eliminating one of Jack's many enemies.{NEWLINE}Redeem value: 200 Jack's Bounty Tokens"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_800_JACK", "Battle Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_800_JACK_DA", "Redeem Battle Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_800_JACK_UFOPEDIA", "{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Gained for winning battles for Jack, Demon Gods be willing.{NEWLINE}Redeem value: 800 Jack's Bounty Tokens"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_50_MUTANT_ALLIANCE", "Humanist Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_50_MUTANT_ALLIANCE_DA", "Redeem Humanist Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_50_MUTANT_ALLIANCE_UFOPEDIA", "{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Gained for eliminating particularly bothersome Humanists.{NEWLINE}Redeem value: 50 Mutant Alliance's Bounty Tokens"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_75_MUTANT_ALLIANCE", "Assassination Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_75_MUTANT_ALLIANCE_DA", "Redeem Assassination Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_75_MUTANT_ALLIANCE_UFOPEDIA", "{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Gained for killing political enemies of the Mutant Alliance.{NEWLINE}Redeem value: 75 Mutant Alliance's Bounty Tokens"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_100_WIZ_BIZ", "Wizardry Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_100_WIZ_BIZ_DA", "Redeem Wizardry Trophy"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_TARGET_100_WIZ_BIZ_UFOPEDIA", "{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Granted for doing dirty work for the Mages.{NEWLINE}Redeem value: 100 Wiz Biz Bounty Tokens."},
		{"STR_TROPHY_GOVT_PRIZE_BIG", "Big Govt Prize"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_GOVT_PRIZE_BIG_UFOPEDIA", "You have earned major appreciation from a Govt official - in the form of a chest, filled with riches.{NEWLINE}(+500 Infamy)"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_DEEP_ONE_DESTROYER", "Deep One Destroyer"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_DEEP_ONE_DESTROYER_PREQ", "Deep One Destroyer (Preq)"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_DEEP_ONE_DESTROYER_UFOPEDIA", "You have thinned the throngs of Deep Ones by no less than 300 specimens, thus rendering a great service to humanity. Congratulations!{NEWLINE}With our expertise thus gained, we might be able to devise an arcane breathing mask, if we possess enough knowledge.{NEWLINE}(+2000 Infamy)"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_ETHEREAL_DESTROYER_PREQ", "Subverter of the gods (Preq)"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_ETHEREAL_DESTROYER", "Subverter of the gods"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_ETHEREAL_DESTROYER_UFOPEDIA", "There is... a bunch of rags in the amount of 33 not very well preserved mantles. How will Nekomimi understand that these are the remains of their enemies? However, it is better not to risk it and send them exactly the mantles of the Star Gods, and not something else. You pack them neatly in the most secure container and hand it over to one of the Smuggler Captains, who is about to fly to the homeworld of Catgirls. Now we have to wait a bit..."},
		{"STR_TROPHY_WORLD_IS_YOURS", "The World Is Yours!"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_WORLD_IS_YOURS_PREQ", "The World Is Yours (Preq)"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_WORLD_IS_YOURS_UFOPEDIA", "You have learned about all the areas of the world, all the types of activities and garnered favors of all your major allies. But most importantly, you have proven you can throw away 1 BILLION DOLAROS like a boss. You have awarded yourself this fabulous prize here. It does nothing, except giving you bragging rights. Congratulations!{NEWLINE}(+2000 Infamy)"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_GAMBLER", "Trophy: Gambler"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_GAMBLER_UC", "              Gambler"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_GAMBLER_PREQ", "Trophy: Gambler (Preq)"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_GAMBLER_UFOPEDIA", "You've become famous for your addiction to gambling, for better or worse!{NEWLINE}(Jack's Favor received){NEWLINE}(+500 Infamy)"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_AT_RIFLE", "Prize: AT Rifle"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_AT_RIFLE_UFOPEDIA", "Jack is impressed with your classy Little Bird and how you resurrected it from a pile of junk metal. Since you have advanced to C-Class Bounty Hunts, and might face heavily armored opponents, he authorized the sale of the Anti-Tank Rifles to help.{NEWLINE}(+200 Infamy)"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_GUN_FREAK", "Gun Collector"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_GUN_FREAK_UFOPEDIA", "You have been recognized by the Gun Almanac magazine as an avid appreciator of fireams and an expert on all things that shoot bullets. The Gun Emporium has in its stock a new weapon, just for you: the Alpha Rifle.{NEWLINE}(+500 Infamy)"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_OLD_EARTH_APPRECIATOR", "Old Earth Appreciator"},
		{"STR_TROPHY_OLD_EARTH_APPRECIATOR_UFOPEDIA", "You have collected remarkable knowledge about the ways of Old Earth. This allows you to buy a very rare handgun from the White Dragon, the Liquidator.{NEWLINE}(+1000 Infamy)"},
