		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_DESCRIPTION", "{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Our recognition grows, as do the expectations! Captain Rank improved!"},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_00_UFOPEDIA", "Right now, we're still generally unknown to the world at large, which is represented by your Captain Rank 0 (Castaway). For each Infamy milestone reached for the first time (next at 2000), your Rank will advance (but only by a single Rank at at time). High ranks may also require additional achievements. Increased worldwide recognition will bring us new opportunities, but also dangers and pressure (Infamy hit at each new Rank)."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_01_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #1 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, know your enemy and yourself!{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 3000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise: Infamy -250."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_02_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #2 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, prove you can gain a trophy befitting it!{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 4000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise: Infamy -250.{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Warning: Your riches are famous enough that someone might tip off the local bandits, causing an instant attack on your Hideout. Reaching the rank of Big Boss will make them too scared to try anymore."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_03_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #3 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, face up to evildoers who are murdering mutants wholesale and become featured in regime's newspapers!{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 5000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise:{NEWLINE}Infamy -250."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_04_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #4 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, interrogate someone important from any of the Big Factions and understand what such importance means!{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 6000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise: Infamy -250.{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Note: Highwaymen patrols will be much more likely to avoid our lands after you achieve the next rank."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_05_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #5 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, interrogate a Faction leader!{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 8000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise: Infamy -500.{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Warning: you have grown big enough to become object of inter-govt envy. Expect sudden attacks on your Hideouts by competing Govt factions. Aim for 'Family Ties' to end this issue."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_06_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #6 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, make Guild and Academy really angry with you!{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 10,000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise: Infamy -500."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_07_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #7 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, interrogate a Faction VIP!{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 12,000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise: Infamy -750."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_08_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #8 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, learn how to defeat the Solar Governor and have the basic means to pursue that goal! You must also learn at least one Faction secret!{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 15,000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise: Infamy -750."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_09_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #9 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, learn all Academy, Church and Guild secrets (up to leader rank).{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 20,000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise: Infamy -1000."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_10_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #10 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, lay down the foundations of world domination, in the air and on the diplomatic scene, and interrogate a Star God who knows something!{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 25,000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise: Infamy -1500.{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Warning: The Solar Governor took notice of the chaos you've created. Star Gods and Mercs will increase their activities."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_11_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #11 Achieved!{NEWLINE}To gain the next rank, master the essence of Star Gods VooDoo tech and Merc secrets!{NEWLINE}Infamy target: 30,000{NEWLINE}Expectations rise: Infamy -2000.{NEWLINE}{NEWLINE}Warning: Star Gods and Mercs will step up their efforts to stamp you down."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_12_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #12 Achieved!{NEWLINE}This is the maximum relevant rank! However, secret ranks exist above it to stoke your ego and people's expectations."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_13_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #13 Achieved!{NEWLINE}You've gained 40,000 Infamy, completed a mission on the Moon and raided a Space Freighter."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_14_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #14 Achieved!{NEWLINE}You've gained 50,000 Infamy and completed a mission on Mars (or its moons)."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_15_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #15 Achieved!{NEWLINE}You've gained 75,000 Infamy and completed a mission outside of the Inner Solar System (Shadowrealms do not count)."},
		{"STR_CAPTAINS_RANK_16_UFOPEDIA", "Captain Rank #16 Achieved!{NEWLINE}You've gained 100,000 Infamy and defeated several Shadow Overlords. This is the true maximum rank."},
