		{"BEES_ARMOR_UFOPEDIA", "Uber Bees Examination. Evasion: REA*30%. NV: 16. ThV: 40%. SENSE: 5. Weapon: Bio, 20 Pwr, attack bottom armor, ignores half armor, damages Freshness, Time Units and Morale."},
